name: Olga Discordia (LORA)
description:
This has become my testing character. As I improve my processes, I will periodically update this model. She is my first Lora and I have things pretty well organized so that I can compare different versions is easily.

You may still prefer the original version. (I think I do, to be honest.) However, if you are wanting more realistic images V6 is a good choice.

You may have seen my previous Olga Discordia Textual Inversion.

I used basically the same process and captions for this. I did add "Olga_Discordia" to the beginning of them all like I saw in a tutorial.
